reviewText: great movies to watch just have to sit for a while

These films are not exactly Oscar-caliber, but they are very entertaining. And given what I paid, they were less than a dollar apiece.  Not bad. Just beware, some of them have a LOT of violence, nudity, and adult situations. They were dubbed from old prints, and there are a few rough spots. But all in all, this was a good bargain.
